      <Description>This dataset contains e active to passive power spectral density ratio when WHISPER is in sounding mode on Cluster 3. 

512 values, one for each frequency, indicating the ratio (Active received power) / (Passive received power), coded as follows :

0: indicate Active/Passive &lt;= 2
 
1: 2 &lt; Active/Passive &lt;= 4 

2: 4 &lt; Active/Passive &lt;= 16 

3: 16 &lt; Active/Passive</Description>
